00:40:39,560 --> 00:40:48,960
It needs a meta rule, a bouncer, that sits above the basic equations and decides which mathematically valid future is actually permitted to become physical reality.

792
00:40:49,100 --> 00:40:50,980
And what does Fliction say that rule is?

