00:41:00,460 --> 00:41:04,080
That's what happens when a heavy fluid sits on top of a light fluid and they violently mix.

796
00:41:04,080 --> 00:41:10,160
Yes. The principle that perfectly matches real-world experiments is called the maximum dissipation rate.

797
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:13,480
Maximum dissipation, meaning getting rid of energy.

