When a measure becomes a target, it ceases to be a good measure.

1090
01:00:15,840 --> 01:00:16,280
Exactly.

1091
01:00:16,440 --> 01:00:22,820
Like if you reward a factory for making more nails, they will just make billions of tiny useless pins to hit the quarter.

1092
01:00:22,980 --> 01:00:25,020
It is exactly that, applied to reality.

1093
01:00:25,020 --> 01:00:36,420
When a system optimizes only for a local metric, the map, and ignores the hidden historical constraints of the underlying reality, the territory, the topological admissibility structure, collapses.

1094
01:00:36,820 --> 01:00:43,360
The system loses track of the causal historical relationships between its own internal components.

1095
01:00:44,000 --> 01:00:45,480
The bundle degenerates.

1096
01:00:45,800 --> 01:00:46,360
It shatters.

1097
01:00:46,800 --> 01:00:46,920
Okay.

